 *  IP address
 *  Latitude/Longitude
 *  Country
 *  Country Code
 *  Region
 *  Region Code (usually empty for Australia)
 *  City
 *  ZIP (which we store under Postal Code)
 *
 * GeoIP City provides:
 *  TBA
 *
 * Google provides:
 *  TBA
 *
 * Note: some of the varchar should be varbinary, see drupal.org/node/1793674
